  ('TN003', 'CAT_HEADPHONE', 'WaveBeat Neckband X', 'Tai nghe choang co nhe, pin 30 gio, chong nuoc IPX5, phu hop tap luyen the thao.', 'https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/54/332588/tai-nghe-truyen-xuong-shokz-openrun-pro-2-s820-den-1-638685550118834054-750x500.jpg', 890000.00, 8, 140, 4.21, 273),
